title: DDFP 273: Ike Taylor & Matt "Money" Smith
itunes:title: DDFP 273: Ike Taylor & Matt "Money" Smith
description:
Shek is joined by Ike Taylor who discusses why he believes Patrick Peterson is a better cornerback than Richard Sherman, debates Calvin Johnson's place in wide receiver history and explains why the Pittsburgh Steelers are Super Bowl contenders this upcoming season. Matt "Money" Smith then joins to discuss LeBron James and music. It's a podcast hit. Take a listen, won't you? 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
